snippet.title: TheSwedishTraveler
snippet.description:
This is a Travelers vlog about different countries, Foreign food, accommodation, and activities.
I have been traveling at least once year, and trying to go to one new country every year. I do travel to London every year as well.
I´m writing a blog as well, on my website at: www.theswedishtraveler.com
